              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 70 cm3 Ge(Li) detector was used for the",
                "activity measurements in Cyclotron Radio Center",
                " (Tohoki Univ.). The samples were placed at a distance",
                "of 20 mm from the detector. The measurement times were",
                "about 75 to 120 hours. The iron dosimetry foils were",
                "measured in the same detector system."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The zirconium-niobium foils were measured at",
                "RTNS-II using a 80 cm3 high purity germanium detector",
                "in 2 or 3 days after taking out the foils."
              ]
            }
